@model SDGApp.ViewModel.UserViewModel
@using (Ajax.BeginForm("ForgetPassword", "Account", new { }, new AjaxOptions { LoadingElementId = "loaderdiv", UpdateTargetId = "divforgetpassword", HttpMethod = "POST" }, new { }))
{
    <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="wrapper">
            @Html.ValidationSummary(true)
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
                    <h4 class="modal-title">Forgot Password ?</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>Enter your e-mail address below to reset your password.</p>
                    @Html.TextBoxFor(m => m.Email, new { @class = "form-control", @placeholder = "Email Address", @autofocus = "" })
                    <span class="text-danger"> @Html.ValidationMessageFor(m => m.Email)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button data-dismiss="modal" class="btn btn-default" type="button">Cancel</button>
                    <button id="btnReset" class="btn btn-success" type="submit">Submit</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
}